00:10:06.669 --> 00:10:10.921
You would probably want to note
that it's a comic use of that

00:10:10.921 --> 00:10:14.646
literary convention,
and so you could say something

00:10:14.646 --> 00:10:18.039
about his deployment of
conventional language,

00:10:18.039 --> 00:10:25.675
either for satirical use or for
comedy or to play up the drama

00:10:25.675 --> 00:10:32.197
of his self-understanding.
So that would be a nicer point,

00:10:32.197 --> 00:10:37.453
a somewhat more subtle
observation, that would set your

00:10:37.453 --> 00:10:43.780
exam-grading TF into a state of
happiness, much to be desired.

